Subject: Secunia Research: DVR Remote ActiveX Control
	DVRobot Library Loading Vulnerability

====================================================================== 

                     Secunia Research 17/11/2011

 - DVR Remote ActiveX Control DVRobot Library Loading Vulnerability -

====================================================================== 
Table of Contents

Affected Software....................................................1
Severity.............................................................2
Description of Vulnerability.........................................3
Solution.............................................................4
Time Table...........................................................5
Credits..............................................................6
